NAME
    Data::Object::Scalar - A Scalar Object for Perl 5

VERSION
    version 0.02

SYNOPSIS
        use Data::Object::Scalar;

        my $scalar = Data::Object::Scalar->new(qr/\w/);

DESCRIPTION
    Data::Object::Scalar provides common methods for operating on Perl 5
    scalar objects.

SEE ALSO
    *   Data::Object::Array

    *   Data::Object::Code

    *   Data::Object::Float

    *   Data::Object::Hash

    *   Data::Object::Integer

    *   Data::Object::Number

    *   Data::Object::Scalar

    *   Data::Object::String

    *   Data::Object::Undef

    *   Data::Object::Universal

